- **IP**: `57.131.46.71` (OVH Ubuntu 24.04)
- **Papka**: `~/qwerty`
- **DB user**: `kinovabot`, **DB**: `kinovadb`
- PostgreSQL tashqaridan yopiq — faqat `localhost`

## Muhim fayllar
- `src/bot.ts` — entry point, bootstrap
- `src/db/postgres.ts` — DB pool, schema, analytics
- `src/handlers/` — text, photo, reels handlerlari
- `src/services/movieService.ts` — kino qidirish logikasi
- `SERVER_SETUP.md` — server konfiguratsiya hujjati
- `scripts/setup-server.sh` — yangi server setup
- `scripts/backup-db.sh` — DB backup (cron: har kuni 03:00)
- `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` — CI/CD

## .env (VPS da qo'lda, git da yo'q)
Asosiy o'zgaruvchilar:
- `BOT_TOKEN` — Telegram bot token
- `DATABASE_URL` — `postgresql://kinovabot:...@localhost:5432/kinovadb`
- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `GEMINI_API_KEY`
- `TMDB_API_KEY`, `OMDB_API_KEY`, `BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY` (ixtiyoriy fallback: `GOOGLE_CSE_KEY` / `GOOGLE_CSE_ID`)

