## DB Schema
`initPostgresSchema()` startup da avtomatik yaratadi:
- `users` — foydalanuvchilar
- `movie_cache` — kino cache
- `analytics_events` — statistika (JSONB)
- `photo_requests`, `reels_requests`, `search_requests` — limitlash
- `pending_identification_feedback` — feedback queue
- `user_activity_day` — kunlik faollik

